    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> We implement this hook in several other components ClearAll, PaginationLink, RefinementListItem, ... We can also take a look at this other components. This hook is an escape hatch in most cases we don't need to implement it. Except when we hit a performance issue.\r\n\r\nUnlike this component, the others don't create issue as far as we know and they have been implemented as part of a general performance. Let's consider the case of the other on case by case basis.",
